cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.NE 

This paper deals with physical scene understanding using both simulation-based and CNN-based models. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves robotics (cs.RO) and neural networks (cs.NE), which are also relevant sub-categories.
